data.description: Water View! Enjoy the view of water from the top deck. No back neighbors and access to a walking trail from the back yard.  This 4 bedroom 2 and half bath with a study home in Top Selling Cinco Ranch is just blocks away from Creech Elementary and just 4 homes down from a play park. The kitchen features an oversize granite island and updated shaker cabinets with soft close drawers. Tiled floors on the 1st floor and updated carpet upstairs. New deck flooring outside the primary bedroom. Highly sought after community with Excellent school district!  Hurry and bring your offer and make this home yours, just in time for the New Year!
